###
### 1. Get dashboard stats (combines multiple aggregations)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 2. Get sales analytics (uses $group with $sum and $avg)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sales
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 3. Get sales analytics with date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/sales?startDate=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 4. Get top-selling products (uses $unwind, $group, $multiply, $lookup)
GET {{baseUrl}}/top-products?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 5. Get category sales report (uses multiple $lookup joins)
GET {{baseUrl}}/category-sales
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 6. Get user order statistics (uses $group with $sum, $avg, $max)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 7. Get order status distribution (uses $group with $sum)
GET {{baseUrl}}/order-status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 8. Get monthly sales trend (uses $month operator)
GET {{baseUrl}}/monthly-trend?year=2026
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 9. Get another user's stats (admin feature)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user-stats/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 10. Access without token (should fail with 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard

###
### 11. Get sales analytics with invalid date (should handle gracefully)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sales?startDate=invalid-date
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
